commit.title: Deprecate "intro_pattern" in tactic notations in favor of "simple_intropattern".
commit.message:
Deprecate "intro_pattern" in tactic notations in favor of "simple_intropattern".

This is to prevent confusion that "intropattern" with the terminology
used in the grammar of tactic in the reference manual.

After some deprecation phase, "intropattern" could be added back to
mean "intropattern".
